{"lemma":"أَتانَيْ","slug":"أَتانَيْ","root":"#.ت.ن","root_slug":"_-ت-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ت-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n147","n148"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%AA%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"she-ass, female donkey, jenny"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *ʔatān-. Cognate with Aramaic אֲתָנָא (ʾăṯānā), אַתָּנָא (ʾattānā), Hebrew אָתוֹן (ʾāṯōn)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n147","headword_ar":"اَتَانٌ","root":"Atn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_itaAnN","text_ar":"اـِتَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) but one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAnapN","text_ar":"اَتَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISk, S, Msb,) or this is of rare occurrence, (K,) occurring in certain of the trads., (IAth,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-ass"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"domestic"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wild"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, M, Msb, K:) pl. (of pauc., T, S, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=tunN","text_ar":"ا=تُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (of mult., T, S, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^utunN","text_ar":"اُتُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^utonN","text_ar":"اُتْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (quasi-pl. n., M) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA^otuwnaA='u","text_ar":"مَاْتُونَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, M, K.) ―         -b2-  Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAnN","text_ar":"اَتَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A foolish and soft"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak woman;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as being likened to a she-ass. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"station of the drawer of water at the mouth of the well;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_itaAnN","text_ar":"اـِتَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rock,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"great mass of stone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, T, S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, T, M;) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the bottom of the casing of a well, so that it is next the water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, T.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large, round mass of rock, which, when it is in shallow water, is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAnu AlD~aHli","text_ar":"اَتَانُ الضَّحلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and a she camel is likened thereto, in respect of her hardness: (S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAnu AlD~aHli","text_ar":"اَتَانُ الضَّحلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a large mass of rock projecting from the water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mass of rock,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large and round, in the water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the mouth of the well, overspread with"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the green substance called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuHolub","text_ar":"طُحْلُب"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it is smooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more smooth than other parts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mass of rock, part of which is immerged"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAmirN","text_ar":"غَامِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and part apparent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAnu Alv~amiyli","text_ar":"اَتَانُ الثَّمِيلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large mass of rock in the interior of the water-course, which nothing raises or moves, of the measure of the stature of a man in length and likewise in breadth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh.) ―         -b4-  Also The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of wood called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAEidap","text_ar":"قَاعِدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is one of four forming the support"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fawodaj","text_ar":"فَوْدَج"},{"kind":"text","text":"[more commonly called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawodaj","text_ar":"هَوْدَج"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=tunN","text_ar":"ا=تُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) with medd. (TA: [but in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AutunN","text_ar":"اُتُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K","ISk","IAth","AA","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n148","headword_ar":"اـِتَانٌ","root":"Atn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAnN","text_ar":"اَتَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}